description:
This Awesome, and one of the kind project has it all----it can be use for your last minute photo intros. This project comes with stunning chrome awesome sideboard frame, particles, flares, and awesome chrome text titles. I have used Optical Flare, plug-in, but you don't have to own it--since I have included 2 projects. A project with plug-ins, and the other without plug-ins. With this one you can insert up to 9 text titles, and 8 Video/Photos of your choice. I have pre-comped most of the layers, so that you can easily add and customize your photos and text titles. To add your photos first, you need to go to the folder called Add Photo Here. Then double click on the pre-comp and drag your footage on top of the &quot; Placeholder Layer&quot; by holding the &quot;Alt or Option&quot; command---this will fit perfectly in the footage box. In addition, you can select the footage layer, so that you can see the footage box. Then click on any corner to resize the footage to fit the screen. To add your text, double click on the folders called Add All Your Text HereÃ¢â‚¬Â¦..double click on the text layer to replace with your own text---and you are all set to go. 1920X1080 Only Sounds Effects Mix Track! are included

